column5: Well folks this will be the last weekend for walleye fishing on the lower grand till the 2nd weekend in may ....so if you got the itch to catch some walleye through the ice this is your weekend to do so ...i will be out testing ice later this eve my guess is there is good ice to fish this weekend ...  Read more: http://fishmaster.proboards.com/thread/4081/last-weekend-walleye-season-grand#ixzz2LXvBJBSq
